reviews.review:
Pros:
-Fun with friends;
-Many builds;
-No chat during matches;
-It works even for solo players.

Cons:
-easy to understand, hard to master, like literally punitive;
-salty community;
-devs don't care about the community or gameplay improvements, like tunnelling, camping, bullying killers, hitboxes (for both killers and survivors), etc.

Would I recommend it? Yes, would I recommend to play it seriously? The hell no!
